data.description: Welcome to 55 E. William Street, a lovely place to call home. This Colonial home offers 4 bedrooms and 2.5 baths. Basement in law or extra suite too! It's everything you've been looking for. To start, you have an open kitchen with plenty of cabinetry for ample storage, new countertop, and backsplash. Natural sunlight floods this space through the beautiful bay window. Adjacent to the kitchen is your living and dining area. This space is bright and open with high ceilings and recessed lighting. Dressed with a neutral palette and new gray laminate flooring. Upgrades include 2.5 baths that have been beautifully redone, and a finished basement with recessed lighting, french doors, and beautiful plank ceramic flooring. This makes a wonderful entertainment area. As you go out to your spacious backyard, you have a nice sized deck to entertain. Located in a warm and friendly neighborhood and only two houses away from the entrance to the Middlesex Greenway with new public bikes for the community's usage. This trail leads a 3.5 mile path into Metuchen and Edison. Close proximity to restaurants, shopping, and public transportation. Don't wait! This home won't last!
